TASKNAME=Tag a local Docker image for pushing to a registry.
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo pull an alpine image.
TASKCOMMAND=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo tags the local image alpine for pushing to a registry. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKVERIFY=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo verify that local image alpine has been tagged.
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove the alpine image.
